[genericglass Collins] Serving Glass: Collins With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1 1/2 oz [genericingredient Bourbon] Jim Beam Bourbon
1/2 oz [genericingredient Southern Comfort] Southern Comfort
1/2 oz [genericingredient Lemon Juice] Lemon Juice
1/2 oz Grenadine
Shake and Strain
Top: Club Soda
Garnish: Cherry
Garnish: Orange Slice

